{"tid":1186987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關破首宗Switch「改機」案　掃蕩黃金商場5店拘5人","createTime":"2019-06-05T10:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:41:49.000Z","uid":75969,"like":87,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"df605ea7eacfc4f94b34633c05db389400c687d0","tid":1186987,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190605/s00001/8633f541b25316be9c8c5b65e4ffef1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F8633f541b25316be9c8c5b65e4ffef1f.jpg&h=4e6747d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190605/s00001/863409640d28de20d4e293c82da85e59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F863409640d28de20d4e293c82da85e59.jpg&h=e24b59a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190605/s00001/863431780f73785f6c49a0031aa11817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F863431780f73785f6c49a0031aa11817.jpg&h=500527ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新一代電子遊戲機的遊戲售價不菲，有不法分子運用硬件破解，為顧客提供玩盜版遊戲的「改機」服務。海關昨日（4日）採取特別行動，於深水埗黃金電腦商場以放蛇方式破獲5間提供任天堂Switch「改機」服務的不法遊戲店，拘捕5名男子，並搜出27套懷疑「規避器件」及110套懷疑侵權遊戲機套裝，市值約21萬元。<br />\n<br />\n海關上月接獲Switch版權持有人任天堂舉報，指深水埗黃金電腦商場有5間店舖提供改機服務，海關經調查後，昨日派出外籍人士喬裝顧客放蛇，其間人員向職員求購Switch遊戲主機，職員游說人員購買售價4600元的「改機」套餐，當中包括價值2000多元的Switch主機、一套用作破解的規避器及一張內附20套盜版遊戲軟件的記憶卡，當中客人可自選3款心水遊戲。人員假裝購買，職員囑人員半小時至一小時後返回店舖取機，又向人員表示玩盜版軟件時切勿關機及使用官方連線功能。<br />\n<br />\n人員見時機成熟，隨即表露身分，當場拘捕5名28至37歲男子，當中兩人為店東。行動中，海關又搜出一批預先載有逾2000款侵權經典遊戲的遊戲機套裝，索價500至3000元不等。<br />\n<br />\n版權及商標科技罪案調查組指揮官吳鎮華表示，是次案件是Swtich推出以來首宗破獲的「改機」案，5間被掃蕩的店舖均沒有商業登記，估計是為方便改名逃避海關追查，而店員亦不會在舖面貼有售賣規避器的資料，5間店舖所使用的規避器屬同款，但暫無證據證明有集團式經營情况。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190605/s00001/1559727773584/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F1559727773584%2F&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKL%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=033c049e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190605%2Fs00001%2F1559727773584%2F&h=dc5844d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190605/s00001/1559727773584/</a>"},{"pid":"6bba82b5f57180512eb56ff5ebfe941b7d686f14","tid":1186987,"uid":1425,"like":73,"dislike":9,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:12:56.000Z","msg":"正評係比海關嘅"},{"pid":"dbeb341fb5f19184679126d3bf85d33680acf59e","tid":1186987,"uid":249604,"like":17,"dislike":137,"score":-120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3475f60dfc91b7dc4bbf7322f937d5a8cd32f2ae","tid":1186987,"uid":25601,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"psp年代又唔見你搞"},{"pid":"f59be4f832bb40cc5a342a54f298aebaf72a673d","tid":1186987,"uid":33868,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:17:28.000Z","msg":"又係老任法務部"},{"pid":"63e4217754c48ea0329229c05974335904c58ced","tid":1186987,"uid":11916,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"dbeb341fb5f19184679126d3bf85d33680acf59e","tid":1186987,"uid":249604,"like":17,"dislike":137,"score":-120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"店主？<br />\n底端詞語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3614bcd61dc14f5bb88dfaec871e2815667390","tid":1186987,"uid":45353,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"老任個代理一樣係黃金開鋪<br />\n<br />\n有無弱智到咁"},{"pid":"c17c75baaf26e80aec4b3648b71bcbc9cc4d45ce","tid":1186987,"uid":1435,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"哇俾多兩千先幫你改機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" cla